attributes.name: Herbs
attributes.description: Herbs are the leaf part of a plant that is used in cooking - these can be used fresh or dried.

attributes.name: Shrubs
attributes.description: Shrub, any woody plant that has several stems, none dominant, and is usually less than 3 m (10 feet) tall.

attributes.name: Trees
attributes.description: Tree is a tall plant that can live a very long time. It has a single stem or trunk and branches that support leaves.
